snippet.textDisplay: I love listening to Nooran Sisters. However, whatever videos I have watched on youtube I always found that in live performances Jyoti's persona overpowers Sultana's presence. But here I found both of them on equal footing and part of that credit goes to the way this song has been arranged in Coke studio. In fact I found Sultana's voice much more appealing. Nevertheless, both of them sang very well and their voices are out of the world.
